<p>These are the steps I used for building MongoDB C driver using Visual Studio  v.11 2012 on Windows:</p>  <ol> <li><code>cd mongo-c-driver-1.1.11</code></li> <li><code>cd src\libbson</code></li> <li><code>cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=C:\usr -G "Visual Studio 10 Win64"</code> .</li> <li><code>msbuild.exe ALL_BUILD.vcxproj</code></li> <li><code>msbuild.exe INSTALL.vcxproj</code></li> <li><code>cd ..</code> , <code>cd..</code></li> <li><code>cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=C:\usr -DBSON_ROOT_DIR=C:\usr -G "Visual Studio 11 2012 Win64"</code> .</li> <li><code>msbuild.exe ALL_BUILD.vcxproj</code></li> <li><code>msbuild.exe INSTALL.vcxproj</code></li> </ol>  <p>It is fine until Step 7. However, Step 8 gives me </p>  <blockquote>   <p><em>Error LNK2019: Unresolved External Symbol</em>. </p> </blockquote>  <p>How do I resolve this?</p>